dct_title_s: Automobile road from San Diego to Imperial Valley
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures, spot heights, and text (grade percentages).
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, waterways, road descriptions.
Indicates distances from San Diego (Grand Hotel) and El Centro.
Numbered 169 and '14 in lower left, 2 in upper right, and 99 in bottom margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
